<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458221779.jpg" alt="1758458221779.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458221779.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458386144.jpg" alt="1758458386144.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458386144.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">烈日下的坚守</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">秋风不燥，日照绿装；歌声嘹亮，漫溢操场。十四连的军训时光，正以昂扬为纸，记录着独属于青春的热血诗行。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458410695.png" alt="1758458410695.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458410695.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458456127.jpg" alt="1758458456127.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458456127.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458519350.jpg" alt="1758458519350.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458519350.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一排帽檐的绝对齐平，划开青春的散漫；一条直线上的无数手肘，定义集体的棱角；一道视线的坚定不移，铸就军人的意志。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">演示动作</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458556297.jpg" alt="1758458556297.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458556297.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458592292.jpg" alt="1758458592292.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458592292.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458609898.jpg" alt="1758458609898.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458609898.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">休整时分，连长亲自示范队列动作，利落的演示让同学们的动作息发标准，烈口悬空，十四连的同学们意志也被磨练的愈发坚定。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">正午的太阳愈发炽热，热浪裹着地面的热气翻涌，汗水从同学们的下颌滴落，打湿了衣襟，在迷彩服上晕出一片片深色水渍。但即便如此，十四连的队列依旧挺拔如峰。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458677762.jpg" alt="1758458677762.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458677762.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458708822.jpg" alt="1758458708822.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458708822.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458729253.jpg" alt="1758458729253.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458729253.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458831575.jpg" alt="1758458831575.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458831575.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">暮色渐浓，训练场上的灯光亮起，给疲惫的一天添了丝柔和。回望这一日，有烈日下的坚守，有训练中的挑战，也有彼此间的鼓励。十四连的同学们用汗水诠释，青春不只有浪漫与憧憬，更有迎难而上的执着与担当。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458927676.jpg" alt="1758458927676.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458927676.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458957672.png" alt="1758458957672.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458957672.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458974635.jpg" alt="1758458974635.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758458974635.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">往后几日，十四连会始终以饱满的斗志迎接每一项训练，用坚持不懈的毅力克服阻碍，让青春风采在军训的磨砺中绽放更夺目的光彩！</span></p>